{"lastModified":1769185320819,"uri":"c::21836669044::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Caribbean Virgin Islands (United States/British Virgin Islands), Bahamas, Caribbean Leewards, Caribbean Windwards, United States of America- Florida East Coast, Canary Islands, United States of America- South East, Caribbean Virgin Islands (United States), Caribbean Virgin Islands (British Virgin Islands)\n\nLuxury 80' Ferretti Yacht Charter in Florida, Bahamas, and The Keys\nSet sail on an extraordinary journey aboard the stunning 80' Ferretti Yacht, a masterpiece of Italian craftsmanship that combines elegance, performance, and modern luxury. Available for charter in the breathtaking waters of Florida, the Bahamas, and the Florida Keys, this 2022-refitted yacht, part of the Ferretti Yachts 780 series, offers an unparalleled experience for up to 12 guests during day cruises or 8 overnight guests. Perfect for everything from a thrilling day trip to an extended getaway, this vessel promises sophistication, comfort, and adventure on the open water.\n\nExquisite Design and Spacious Layout\nThe 80' Ferretti showcases a sleek, aerodynamic profile with a deep-V hull, ensuring stability and a smooth ride even in choppy waters. Its exterior features expansive teak decking, a spacious flybridge with panoramic views, and multiple lounging areas perfect for dining, sunbathing, or socializing. Large floor-to-ceiling windows flood the interior with natural light, enhancing the sense of space and connection to the surrounding seascape.\n\nThe main salon is a blend of contemporary elegance and timeless luxury, appointed with fine woods, plush fabrics, and polished finishes. It includes a comfortable lounge area, a formal dining space, and a state-of-the-art Bluetooth sound system for immersive entertainment. The flybridge is a standout, offering a hot tub, a wet bar, and ample seating for unforgettable sunset cruises or lively gatherings. The aft deck is ideal for al fresco dining, while the foredeck provides sun pads for ultimate relaxation.\n\nLuxurious Accommodations\nThe yacht’s four staterooms are designed for comfort and privacy, accommodating up to 8 overnight guests. Each cabin features en-suite bathrooms, climate control, and luxurious amenities. The master suite is a highlight, boasting a king-size bed, panoramic windows, and ample storage for a serene retreat. The additional cabins—one queen, one full, and one twin side-by-side—are equally well-appointed, ensuring all guests enjoy a restful and indulgent stay. The 2022 refit enhances the interiors with modern finishes and cutting-edge technology, making this one of the finest Ferretti 780s available for charter.","blueprint":{"name":"DESTINY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::45844060-8d84-11f0-978c-e7a6d9f82da0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::45c4f2e0-8d84-11f0-978c-e7a6d9f82da0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4583cb30-8d84-11f0-978c-e7a6d9f82da0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::457c7830-8d84-11f0-bd8f-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::45813320-8d84-11f0-978c-e7a6d9f82da0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::457d3b80-8d84-11f0-bd8f-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::457e9b10-8d84-11f0-bd8f-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::457e4cf0-8d84-11f0-bd8f-5550877256eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d81-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::45863c30-8d84-11f0-978c-e7a6d9f82da0/{imageVariant}",